05.07.2008
1. change stupid error in tables name - mallarchive_* change to mailarchive_*
   run this sql-commands:
    RENAME TABLE `mallarchive_msginfo` TO `mailarchive_msginfo` ;
    RENAME TABLE `mallarchive_recipient` TO `mailarchive_recipient` ;
2. improve search mail. now use mailarchive_recipient table where stored only
   rcpt-to information about mail
3. improve archimport.php script for insert statistics about mail into
   special mysql table
4. fix error in "auto-clean" code. Instead of clearing the contained letter, 
   there was its full removal.

05.07.2008
1. At sending the letter to the manager old headings FROM and TO are replaced 
  on X-OLD-FROM and X-OLD-TO 
2. At import of the letter in mysql in the special mysql table record for 
  statistics is done. Then by means of special scripts it is possible to 
  deduce statistics on a corporate site for users.
3. The small instruction on installation is written. Covers not all aspects, 
  but now it is more clear as it to establish on a server
4. Write email RCPT-TO into special table for improve speed of seek e-mail.

